  "title": "Customer Service Coordinator | 5.25 days | Jurong East | Training Provided - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><strong>Customer Service Coordinator</strong><br /><br />Basic Salary: $2,000 - $2,600 + AWS & variable Bonus<br />Working Days: Mon to Fri: 9am - 5:30pm, Alt Sat: 9am - 1 pm<br />Address: Jurong East</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide customer service support via phone and email.</li><li>Attend to Customer’s enquires on product, RFQ and deliveries.</li><li>Preparing of shipping document and import/export documentation.</li><li>Monitor and ensure outgoing shipments being delivered as prescribed.</li><li>Monitor and ensure incoming shipments being cleared timely.</li><li>Processing of invoice promptly.</li><li>Extract and tabulate data for report analysis using Microsoft Office Suite.</li><li>Ensure Key Performance Indexes are met for all incoming and outgoing activities.</li><li>Coordinate with supervisor for warehouse activities.</li><li>Collaborate with other departments to fulfill orders and ensure timely deliveries.</li><li>Ensure accuracy of all inventories. Maintain accurate records of inventory levels and report any discrepancies.</li><li>Performing of general housekeeping within the workplace and maintaining of a safe working environment.</li><li>Perform any other duties as and when assigned by the Management.</li></ul><p><br />Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
